RecordCountCheckSumForm is a Form
    Layout
        two column
            RecordCount
                label is "UnrestoredRecordCount"
                display only
                display as tag
                    color of orange when (DataPossiblyNotSent)
                    color of red when (DisplayRedAlert)
                    color of green when (DisplayGreenAlert)
                display zero
            visible when (DataPossiblyNotSent)
                text of "ArchivedDataRecordsEitherDoNotExistOrThereAreRecordsThatHaveNotBeenSentToTheArchive"
                    color of orange
        RecordCountCheckSum
            display only
